Flowing Heritage - The Indian Water Narrative

We stepped in and experienced the essence of the stepwell- a rhythm, a quiet pulse, a sanctuary between worlds. It was a multidisciplinary craft-art exhibition, curated by @anjanasomany at @arthshila_delhi 

Exploring India’s profound connection with water, the experience weaved history, culture, and craft together through tactile and tech-aided installations, layered sounds, and luminous visuals. It was beautiful to see how they presented the many stories of India brought down through generations in creative ways that truly enthralled the senses.

Exhibitions like these are a testament to the power of art and storytelling, beautifully bridging India’s rich heritage with contemporary expression, deserving every bit of celebration for their thoughtful and inspiring curation.

#artexhibition #water #naturelovers #heritageofindia #celebrateindia #ourworld
